{"type": "article", "id": 25000, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-04-06T07:19:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 1954, "name": "包装"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115805HjI5VDbX0UTS2n6e.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>Shift Chair by Jonas Forsman &amp;  Moooi</h2>\n<p>这是瑞典设计师 Jonas Forsman 为荷兰品牌  Moooi 推出的折叠椅，可以收成一个平面立在墙边以适应越来越小的居住空间。他采用了 3D 编织技术制作了椅子的靠背，很有弹性，椅子的座位则是一个软垫，收起来的时候正好收进了靠背的凹槽中。椅子的形态宽阔而舒适，有多种颜色搭配，很居家。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153940imJKItL7UxMZ4eq5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153941OupqJKgYR2PCW1U7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071539413LGeo9JOUznmxPv6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6741453\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153942Y57nZ3oicTfjwWB0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56303419\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153942NG9qPbZgwX5Q2TL0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153943v3WdAjUZyz9E7h62.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Sway tables by Nendo</h2>\n<p>这是 Nendo 最新推出的大理石边桌，有高低两种，桌面和桌腿方正却都是向着左或右倾斜，从正面看是一个平行四边形，给人一种快要塌下来的错觉。设计师想要探索大理石材料的轻盈和灵活。桌子有黑白两色，是为意大利品牌 Marsotto edizioni 而设计，即将在米兰家具展上展出。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071539438QWP3x4oRBbjnSEy.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69230769\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153944OzstjQmJgvHbloKy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153944No7iF0wyhRtLlUue.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153945flNsd2xTy0L1Hcwj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153945EtXgmauvOD1HoQMk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>tracer by ETT</h2>\n<p>这辆电动自行车的零件可以 3D 打印，它允许用户自己在网站上下载文件打印零件以更换。这些零件包括后挡泥板、挡泥板支架和前制动闸等结构，而它的主要结构是用铝合金做的，与原本轻盈的结构对比，看起来很酷，它也有提高行驶速度的功能。内有 42V 锂离子供电，3 小时充电后可行驶 97 公里。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153946HsKlvkQcrzD3Wm6p.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153946fygLdjDaF1OPXZqo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153947jm2FCEUBlx9wbHqO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153947vNGarYOiFfIt47Wz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153948phsaPtJTbdUzCwNS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>ILO Clam Shell Dish Drainer by SCOTT JARVIE</h2>\n<p>这是一个可以放餐具的盘子，它也有漏水的功能。盘子中间小山一样的圆锥是用来隔离餐具的，而四周的三角边可以嵌上餐盒或挂上杯子，成为一个小的收纳。盘子下面的四个支撑脚可以替换两种长短的脚垫，用来转换蓄水和倒水，当积累到一定程度时就可沿着出水口倒出。<a href=\"http://www.lakeland.co.uk/p24730/ILO-Clam-Shell-Dish-Drainers\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153949DSgzHLayEl8BjXZh.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153949bc34j1QfGTDZO7zu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153950yS1Z7z4wc0rCvFGf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071539500V6MRLKBnroTIO2g.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153951uqUZd67XG0xKk4n1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153951rn8qPUb9NtMXTFpW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h2>Nuvola by Byeongjun Kim &amp; 三星</h2>\n<p>这是三星推出的一个伞架的概念设计，它有上下两个缺口分别放直杆雨伞和折叠雨伞，伞架的凹槽可以聚集雨伞流过的水并干燥。它更重要的设计是上面的天气情况显示屏，有天气预报的功能，提醒你该拿伞了。伞架的两侧是不完全对称的曲线轮廓，有助于凸显轻盈和现代感。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153952NXuZIf5L9t0DHOJU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153952s82JaMXtNDCPmndb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153953bWsBHf71xURwF8KO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153953jdbUmWw8PVNnki7z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153953tSCljJnGZ4OhMT19.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071539540SOWzIM6QqVPmc8Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Noam by Acne</h2>\n<p>Noam 啤酒致力于重拾德国巴伐利亚啤酒口感，他们找到来自北欧的 Acne 设计包装。瓶身刻有一圈竖条状的凹槽，就像是古典圆柱上的样式，看起来更加细长，搭配黄色的啤酒后更显典雅珍贵。透过瓶子可以清晰看到气泡，而经过冰镇后的水珠则会顺着凹槽流下去，非常清爽。<a href=\"http://eyeondesign.aiga.org/happy-hour-clever-tactile-beer-wine-packaging/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153955YZKR8UIiktNwQvgA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153955Skpilv3zU7I8naAM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3725\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153956aO10gfum82EVFqrG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153956Ds9o6lWI1rpqCcjK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.18148148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}